OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,FMeningitis B survivor Lisa Shoko tells
OL,7,FITV News Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,8,FBarry about her ordeal and why she
OL,9,Fthinks the NHS should start offering
OL,10,Ffree vaccinations against meningitis B
OL,11,Fto teenagers
OL,13,FFor Lisa Shoko, the recent meningitis
OL,14,Foutbreak in Kent was painfully
OL,15,Freminiscent.
OL,17,FIn 2015, Lisa was an excited and
OL,18,Fambitious law student in her first
OL,19,Fyear at the University of Kent. But
OL,20,Feverything changed that winter when
OL,21,Fshe suddenly got a headache.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,FAt first, Lisa dismissed it as a
OL,7,Fmigraine, but then came sensitivity to
OL,8,Flight, a fever and aching muscles,
OL,9,Funtil she collapsed. She lay
OL,10,Funconscious on her bathroom floor for
OL,11,Fhours before she was eventually found
OL,12,Fby her housemate.
OL,14,FLisa, who was 18 years old at the
OL,15,Ftime, has no memory of what followed,
OL,16,Fbut doctors and her family prepared
OL,17,Ffor the worst as she spent more than a
OL,18,Fweek in a life-threatening condition
OL,19,Fin intensive care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,FWhile she survived meningitis B, Lisa
OL,7,F- who was once a talented public
OL,8,Fspeaker and tennis player - would
OL,9,Fnever be the same person again.
OL,11,FBrain fog and memory loss made
OL,12,Fstudying impossible.
OL,14,F"I failed my first year of university
OL,15,Fbecause I simply couldn't keep up,"
OL,16,FLisa told ITV News. "Coming out of
OL,17,Fmeningitis I had a severe stammer, I
OL,18,Fcouldn't speak without hesitation, I'd
OL,19,Flost my confidence completely."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,FIt turned out that surviving the
OL,7,Finfection was only her first hurdle.
OL,9,F"I felt isolated and anxious. For
OL,10,Fyears after experiencing meningitis, I
OL,11,Ffelt extremely depressed, watching
OL,12,Feveryone else that you know move
OL,13,Fforward with their lives.
OL,15,F"You might not see it physically, but
OL,16,Fyou don't realise how much harder I
OL,17,Fhave to work."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,FLisa eventually managed to complete
OL,7,Fher degree, but wants other young
OL,8,Fpeople to be protected against the
OL,9,Flifelong impact of this dangerous
OL,10,Fdisease.
OL,12,FShe believes the NHS should start
OL,13,Foffering free vaccinations against
OL,14,Fmeningitis B to teenagers.
OL,16,F"I think it should be rolled out on
OL,17,Fthe NHS, I think it should be
OL,18,Faccessible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,FThe Meningitis Research Foundation has
OL,7,Fanalysed the most recent annual data
OL,8,Ffrom the four nations of the UK and
OL,9,Fshared the findings exclusively with
OL,10,FITV News.
OL,12,FAcross the UK, there were 475 annual
OL,13,Fcases of invasive meningococcal
OL,14,Fdisease. And, overwhelmingly, the B
OL,15,Fstrain was the leading cause - that's
OL,16,Fthe same type we saw in the Kent
OL,17,Foutbreak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,FIn fact, in England and Northern
OL,7,FIreland, it accounted for 100% of
OL,8,Fcases in teenagers. Scotland and Wales
OL,9,Fdon't publish the data by age group.
OL,11,FThe MenB vaccine is offered on the NHS
OL,12,Fto babies, but protection is not
OL,13,Flifelong. Teenagers can get a free
OL,14,Fvaccine against the A, C, W and Y
OL,15,Fstrains of the bacteria.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,FBut further protection against MenB
OL,7,Fhas to be paid for privately, costing
OL,8,Fup to #300 for the two doses.
OL,10,FSome experts say this shows a worrying
OL,11,Fprotection gap for teens and young
OL,12,Fadults. The Meningitis Research
OL,13,FFoundation is calling for an NHS
OL,14,Fimmunisation programme against Men B
OL,15,Ffor this at-risk age group.
OL,17,F"Meningitis has not gone away in the
OL,18,FUK, and it is prevalent amongst this
OL,19,Fage group," Vinny Smith, chief
OL,20,Fexecutive of Meningitis Research
OL,21,FFoundation, told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,F"They are the future of this country.
OL,7,FWe're looking at an age group that is
OL,8,Fnot protected, when they could be. In
OL,9,Fthis day and age, that doesn't make
OL,10,Fany sense to me."
OL,12,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,13,Fspokesperson said: "The Secretary of
OL,14,FState has asked the Joint Committee on
OL,15,FVaccination and Immunisation (JVCI)
OL,16,Ffor an updated recommendation on
OL,17,FMeningococcal B vaccination based on
OL,18,Fthe latest evidence, including from
OL,19,Fthe recent outbreak in the Canterbury
OL,20,Farea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777619131
OL,3,C'I survived deadly meningitis, but was
OL,4,Cleft with brain fog and depression'
OL,6,F"The JCVI is reviewing eligibility,
OL,7,Fhave provided the Meningitis Research
OL,8,FFoundation with the opportunity to
OL,9,Fsubmit evidence as part of that review
OL,10,Fand will provide further updates in
OL,11,Fdue course.
OL,13,F"The UK has a world-leading national
OL,14,Fimmunisation programme which is
OL,15,Fregularly reviewed and updated to
OL,16,Freflect the changing nature of
OL,17,Finfectious diseases and provide the
OL,18,Fbest protection and outcomes for the
OL,19,Fpublic."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
